*   ## **_BRON BREAKKER DEF. LOCAL TALENT BY BRUTALIZING HIM UNTIL REF RINGS THE BELL._**
    
      
    Breakker attacks the jobber until the bell rings and continues to beat on him well after. Breakker spears the poor fella out of the referees hands then squished his head with a steel chair against the steps.
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e14aa414-021e-4f86-88d7-346bf365e401/GOEFB4RXkAAJ9r3.jpg?format=original)

"You can't control me. You didn't put me in King of the Ring. That's on you." - Bron Breakker to Adam Pearce

