*   ## WORLD TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: AWESOME TRUTH DEF. JUDGEMENT DAY
    

R-Truth had mentioned he got Andre the Giant to help out tonight. It turns out it was Braun Strowman.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/099fceb2-d580-463d-a7ac-d2be5fea9c5f/Screenshot+2024-05-20+185624.jpg?format=original)

Sami Zayn was going to dismiss Otis' apology for interfering in the match with Gable. But he understands that Otis is a good guy who listened to the wrong person.

He tells Otis to stop listening to Gable and start listening to the fans and his own heart.

